(
"WTemplateID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"RentTemplateID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"ChargeCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"ChargeName" NVARCHAR2(100) not null,

"StartTime" TIMESTAMP default SYSDATE not null,
"EndTime" TIMESTAMP,
"Enable" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP default SYSDATE not null,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32) not null,
"ModifyTime" TIMESTAMP,
"ModifyBy" NUMBER(32),
constraint PK_CON_WARRANTYTEMPLATE primary key ("WTemplateID")
);
